entries.body:
On Windows, the ANSI encoding can convert fullwidth characters into regular ones. Fullwidth double quotes U+FF02 (＂) are substituted in place of regular U+0022 ("), bypassing escapeshellarg.
Example of vulnerable code:
  $url = "https://example.tld/" . $_GET['path'] . ".txt";
  system("wget.exe -q " . escapeshellarg($url));
Path payload: ＂ --use-askpass=calc ＂
